rooms.Name: Under the Bridge
rooms.Description:
The arch under the bridge is covered by seaweed for one foot above the
surface of the river.  The water gently flows through an opening in the lower
part of the city wall.

ExtraDescs.Description:
It is built from large grey rocks that have been fastened to each other with
some kind of mortar.  Looks pretty solid.

rooms.Name: On the River
rooms.Description:
North of here you see the miserable buildings of the poor alley.  The
river flows west towards the bridge.  The riverbanks are too steep to climb.

rooms.Name: On the River
rooms.Description:
North of here you see the dump.  The river flows from east to west.  The
riverbanks are too steep to climb.

rooms.Name: On the River
rooms.Description:
The levee is directly north of here.  The river flows in an east west
direction.

rooms.Name: On the River
rooms.Description:
You see the warehouse on the northern riverbank.  East of here you see the
city wall.  The river flows west towards the levee.

rooms.Name: On the River
rooms.Description:
The river enters from a hole in the eastern city wall.  The hole has been
blocked by several vertically positioned iron bars set into the wall.

Exits.Description:
The iron bars make it impossible to pass through the hole in the wall.
Beyond the bars you see the great plains.

rooms.Name: On the River
rooms.Description:
You are just slowly floating downt he river, nice and lazy like.  The breeze
ruffles your hair and you just chill out.

rooms.Name: A faster flowing section of the river
rooms.Description:
You are on a wider, faster flowing portion of the river, there is a large
barge heading your way.  I would advise moving around it as the captain 
can not see you.

rooms.Name: IN THE PATH OF THE BARGE, IF YOU ARE A NEWBIE, DO NOT COME HERE!!!
rooms.Description:
You are in the direct path of the barge.  Its currect won't allow you to
swim out of the way, you have to fight him now, or swim MUCH FASTER!!!

rooms.Name: Around the barge
rooms.Description:
Wow, that barge would have hurt if you hadn't swam over here...ahead there
is a large port with parked barges and so on.  The port smells real
funny as well.

rooms.Name: On the River, Before the Port of New Sparta
rooms.Description:
You are floating along and the current has pulled here.  You had it planned
all along :)  There is a really nasty smell, but, you made it.

rooms.Name: The other side of the river
rooms.Description:
You are standing on the other side of the river.  There is tall grass
et cetera growing everywhere.  You can see a dirt road beginning on
the this side of the river.

rooms.Name: A dirt road
rooms.Description:
You are standing on a dirt road.  There are trees and son on surrounding
the area.  You can here nature making its normal noises.

rooms.Name: Standing on a well, looking over the county
rooms.Description:
You are standing on top of the well, looking over the county.  To the north
you can see midgaard, to the south you can see a farm.

rooms.Name: A field
rooms.Description:
You are standing in a small field, you here bugs and stuff tweeting 
and so on.

rooms.Name: Falling down the well, this is a DT!
rooms.Description: You are falling down the well, this is gonna HURT like a bitch!

rooms.Name: A long path heading toward a barn
rooms.Description:
You are on a long path heading toward a barn, a smell of animal poop
reigns throughout the area.  There is a wind that is blowing across you
from right to left.  There is tall grass that is growing all around you.

rooms.Name: A long path heading toward a barn
rooms.Description:
You are on a long path heading toward a barn, a smell of animal poop
reigns throughout the area.  There is a wind that is blowing across you
from right to left.  There is tall grass that is growing all around you.

rooms.Name: Lost in the tall grass
rooms.Description: You seem to be lost in the tall grass, it is so high you can't see anything.

rooms.Name: Just outside the barn
rooms.Description:
You are standing just outside the Duke family barn.  It is white, there is
a large car sitting in the middle of the room.  It is orange with the
# 01 on it.  On the hood is the confederate flag.  There is an old man
here working on something and grumbling.

rooms.Name: Within the barn
rooms.Description:
You are standing within the barn, the car that you saw, dominates the center
of the room. There is a man here in a blue jumper and a red hate, grumbling.

rooms.Name: Up in the barn
rooms.Description:
You are in the loft of the barn, Bo and Luke have been shovelling hay
all day long.  They are wondering what the hell you are doing in
their loft.

rooms.Name: The road in front of the Duke farm
rooms.Description:
You are standing on the road that leads out of the Duke farm.  There are
chickens and what not that are running around here.

rooms.Name: Road into downtown Hazzard
rooms.Description:
You are on the road into Hazzard county, you can see a cop car in a ditch
to the south of here.

rooms.Name: On a road into hazzard county
rooms.Description: You are on the main road into hazzard county.

rooms.Name: A fork in the road
rooms.Description:
You see a fork in the road, both ways seem the same.  It is your call as
to which way to go, you realize though that somewhere west of here
lies Chickesaw county.

rooms.Name: a paved road
rooms.Description:
You are standing on a paved road, this is definately the road the Chickesaw,
I would leave now before Sherieff Little catches you!

rooms.Name: a dirt road
rooms.Description:
You are on the road that definitely runs into Hazzard county, you see a
tow truck ahead of you, fixing a car.

rooms.Name: a dirt road
rooms.Description:
You are standing on what appears to be a stick up!  Better flee now before
the thugs get you!

rooms.Name: Outside of downtown hazzard.
rooms.Description:
You are standing just within the city limits.  There are building and what
not around you.  Since this is a TV show, all the buildings are fake but
one.  And that is right in front of you.

rooms.Name: Outside of city hall: Hazzard County
rooms.Description:
You are standing outside a large white building, there are people walking
around and doing what not.  Inside you see a lot of stuff and a large fat
buddy standing there gloating.

rooms.Name: Within City Hall: Hazzard County
rooms.Description:
You are standing within city hall of Hazzard county.  You see a large fat
man standing here, smoking a cigar and thinking of the duke's farm.

rooms.Name: A sand barge
rooms.Description: You have come apon a sand barge in the middle of the river

rooms.Name: Quick-Sand
rooms.Description:
As you look down, you realize you are sinking, but as you move your feet,
you realize that this stuff isn't as potent as you think..as you descend
your feet hit something hard, like stairs.

rooms.Name: HOLD YER BREATHE!
rooms.Description:
You are now almost engulfed in the quicksand, you realize there is no
escape now, you must continue down the steps.

rooms.Name: a hole
rooms.Description: This seems to be a hole into some lost room.

rooms.Name: A hidden room
rooms.Description:
You seem to be in some sort of ruins or something.  As you look forward, there
are shadows dancing everywhere.

rooms.Name: In the center of the room
rooms.Description: You are standing in what is clearly some sort of temple.

rooms.Name: Before an altar
rooms.Description:
You are standing before a great altar, there seems to be a corpse lying
apon it.

rooms.Name: Climbing up onto the altar
rooms.Description: You are climbing onto the altar

rooms.Name: On the altar
rooms.Description:
You are standing upon the altar.  There is some wierd square, with a keyhole
on the surface of the altar.

rooms.Name: Climbing down the altar
rooms.Description: You are climbing down the altar, you see someone standing before you.

rooms.Name: Behind the altar
rooms.Description:
You stand behind the altar of Death.  Here resides the queen of power.
The scales riple along her back as you enter.  She is insulted by your
pathetic mortalness.  Even the IMP Sheol fears her power over him.  She
has lost her pet Tiamat and sees you as something that can keep her busy
for a round or 2.

rooms.Name: Entrance to the Great Temple of Asgaard
rooms.Description:
You are standing before a wall with a door.  Above the door lies
the the letter Temple of Asgaard
There are 2 large guardian statues that stand blankly before you.
The seem to form the columns that would have held up a roof.  Instead
of their being a roof.  There is a ceiling of sand.  The doors stand about
25 feet tall, but are glowing brightly.

rooms.Name: Within the Great Temple of Asgaard
rooms.Description:
You are standing just within the temple doors.  Before you, you see
a city in ruins.  These were the last vistages of the people that lived
before the great destruction.  Before you lies what appears to be the
main street.

rooms.Name: Central walkway
rooms.Description:
You are walking down the central walkway.  Before you lies this lost
city.  Far ahead is the main temple.

rooms.Name: Central Walkway
rooms.Description:
You are on the central walkway.  There are empty houses and piles of bones
everywhere.  Everything you see here is glowing with a bright light.

rooms.Name: Entrance to a small temple
rooms.Description:
You are standing outside a small temple.  The doors are closed and
bolted from the inside.
The facade of the building is rusted and withered.

rooms.Name: Realm of the Dead
rooms.Description: You are standing in the ethereal realm of the Dead.
